bilingual.source: Choose a country that you are all interested in.
bilingual.target: 选择一个你们都感兴趣的国家。

bilingual.source: They were happy to talk to the interested audience.
bilingual.target: 他们很乐意与感兴趣的观众交谈。

bilingual.source: I recommend the book for all who are interested in galaxies.
bilingual.target: 我推荐这本书给所有对星系感兴趣的人。

bilingual.source: But I am more interested to see the pandas in the Wolong Panda Reserve.
bilingual.target: 但我更感兴趣的是看卧龙熊猫保护区的熊猫。

bilingual.source: Aron Ralston is an American man who is interested in mountain climbing.
bilingual.target: 阿伦·拉尔斯顿是一位对登山感兴趣的美国人。

bilingual.source: At lunch, I like to check some online forums about topics I'm interested in.
bilingual.target: 午餐时，我喜欢查看一些我感兴趣的在线论坛。

bilingual.source: This book caters to those interested in history.
bilingual.target: 这本书迎合那些对历史感兴趣的人。

bilingual.source: You can skip to the content you are interested in.
bilingual.target: 你可以换页到你感兴趣的内容。

bilingual.source: He circled the ads that interested him in the newspaper.
bilingual.target: 他在报纸上圈出了感兴趣的广告。

bilingual.source: The app is targeting users who are interested in fitness.
bilingual.target: 这个应用程序瞄准了对健身感兴趣的用户。

list.abstract: interested（英[ˈɪntrəstɪd]，美[ˈɪntrəstɪd]），英语单词，形容词，意思为好奇的；关注的；感兴趣的。短语搭配有be interested in（对…感兴趣），例句为“He is interested in Spring Festival.（他对春节感兴趣。）” interested形容词类近义词有prejudiced，相关反义词有bore、uninterested。

yingyinNormal.en: I've got very interested. Enraged.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是非常感兴趣的表情。暴怒的表情。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm working on my facial expressions. See, I've got interested.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我正在练习我的面部表情。看，这是我感兴趣的表情。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I know I'm here to discuss a topic Lady Grantham is interested in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只知道我是来讨论一个老夫人感兴趣的话题。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. That's fine. But I think that you might be really interested in our second model.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的，这很好，并且我认为我们的第二款产品，会让你非常感兴趣的

yingyinNormal.en: We never lost you, Doctor. We've kept our distance. Even helped keep some other interested parties off your scent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们一直在关注你，博士，但是保持着距离，甚至暗地里把一些对你感兴趣的人。挡了下来。

yingyinNormal.en: It's designed to repackage comments and gossip by others and disperse it onto sites so it can drive interested users back to Scabbit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它是将其他人的流言蜚语重新整合并散布在网站上，从而将感兴趣的用户吸引到「瞎掰网」来。

yingyinNormal.en: The only future I'm interested in is the next four years. So, yes, I'm selling tomorrow and the day after that and the day after that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我唯一感兴趣的未来就是接下来的四年。所以没错，我明天要推销后天接着推销大后天还要推销。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm more interested in what you have to offer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我更想知道你能开出什么价码。

yingyinNormal.en: You think you might be interested? Absolutely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这下你有兴趣吗？绝对有。

yingyinNormal.en: Is your boyfriend interested in clever, Jenny?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的男友在意你的聪明吗，珍妮。

yingyinNormal.en: I know. But you're also not the only interested party.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道，但也并不是就你对这个感兴趣。

yingyinNormal.en: It isn't very interesting. But you two are interested.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很无趣的东西。但是你俩兴致挺浓的。

yingyinNormal.en: That's really not the sort of thing we're interested in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们对这类事情不感兴趣。

yingyinNormal.en: And the students basically were not interested in those.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些受访学生大部分对这些不感兴趣。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, that's not it. Stuart's kind of interested in Amy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要说的不是这个，斯图尔特对艾米感兴趣。

yingyinNormal.en: Won't happen. He is not interested in anything but physics.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不可能，他除了物理以外什么都没有兴趣。

yingyinNormal.en: And a thousand dollars. Is something I'm very interested in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一千美金。对此我很感兴趣！

yingyinNormal.en: There was a chapter on visualization that really interested me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有一章关于想象的令我很感兴趣。

yingyinNormal.en: It's the same reason I'm interested in your big, flat feet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我对你的扁平巨足感兴趣也是这个原因。

yingyinNormal.en: Can we drop this? I am not interested in the guy's apartment.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别说了，好吗？我对那家伙的公寓没兴趣。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Millennials may not be that <highlight>interested</highlight> in taking their place.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 千禧一代可能没那么有兴趣取代他们的位置。

examination_example.sentence: Giving more children this training could increase the number of people <highlight>interested</highlight> in the field and help fill the jobs gap, Corina said.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 科里纳说，给更多的孩子提供这种培训可以增加对这一领域感兴趣的人数，并有助于填补就业缺口。

examination_example.sentence: Belgium is <highlight>interested</highlight> mainly in the effects of poverty on Belgium.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 比利时主要感兴趣的是贫困对其的影响。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
